      <a href="/episodes/104-exception-notifications-revised">Exception Notifications (revised)</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Few things are worse than seeing a &quot;Something went wrong&quot; 500 error on your production application. Here I show how to be notified when this happens using exception_notification and mention several other alternatives.
